\c 3
\s Umsebenzi kaJohane uMbhabhathizi
\p
\v 1 Kwathi ngomnyaka wetshumi lanhlanu wokubusa kukaTiberiyosi uKesari\x + Mat. 22.17.\x*, uPontiyusi Pilatu engumbusi weJudiya\x + 2.2.\x*, loHerodi\x + Mat. 14.1. Mark. 6.14 & 8.15. Luka 3.19. 8.3; 9.7,9; 13.31; 23.7. Seb. 4.27.\x* \w engumtetrarki\w** weGalili\x + Mat. 14.1. Luka 3.19. 9.7. Seb. 13.1.\x*, loFiliphu umfowabo engumtetrarki weIturiya lelizweni iTrakoniti, loLisaniya engumtetrarki weAbilene\x + 3.19. Mat. 14.3. Mark. 6.17.\x*,
\v 2 uAnasi\x + Joha. 18.13,24. Seb. 4.6.\x* loKayafasi bengabapristi abakhulu\x + Mat. 26.3.\x*, ilizwi likaNkulunkulu lafika kuJohane\x + Mat. 3.1-12. Mark. 1.2-8.\x* indodana kaZakariya\x + 1.13.\x* enkangala\x + 1.80.\x*.
\v 3 Wasesiza esigabeni sonke seJordani esizingelezeleyo, etshumayela ubhabhathizo lokuphenduka kube yikuthethelelwa kwezono\x + 1.77.\x*;
\v 4 njengokulotshiweyo egwalweni lwamazwi kaIsaya umprofethi, ukuthi: Ilizwi lomemezayo enkangala \add lithi\add*: Lungisani indlela yeNkosi; qondisani indledlana zayo.
\v 5 Sonke isigodi sizagqitshwa, layo yonke intaba loqaqa kuzakwehliswa; njalo kuzaqondiswa amazombazombe, lamaxhakaxhaka ezindlela azalungiswa\x + Isa. 40.3,4.\x*;
\v 6 layo yonke inyama\x + Isa. 52.10. 40.5. Luka 2.10. Hlab. 98.2.\x* izabona usindiso lukaNkulunkulu\x + 2.30. Seb. 28.28.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Ngakho wathi emaxukwini aphumela ukubhabhathizwa nguye: Nzalo yezinyoka, ngubani olixwayise ukubalekela ulaka oluzayo?
\v 8 Ngakho thelani izithelo ezifanele ukuphenduka; njalo lingaqali ukuthi phakathi kwenu\x + 5.21; 13.25,26; 14.9. Mat. 26.22.\x*: SiloAbrahama ongubaba \add wethu\add*; ngoba ngithi kini: UNkulunkulu ulamandla okumvusela uAbrahama abantwana kulamatshe\x + 16.24,30. 19.9.\x*.
\v 9 Lakhathesi lehloka selibekiwe empandeni zezihlahla; ngakho sonke isihlahla esingatheli isithelo esihle siyaganyulwa siphoselwe emlilweni.
\p
\v 10 Amaxuku asembuza, athi: Pho thina sizakwenzani\x + 3.12,14. Seb. 2.37. Seb. 9.6; 16.30; 22.10.\x*?
\v 11 Wasephendula wathi kubo: Olezembatho ezimbili, kamuphe ongelaso; lolokudla kenze njalo\x + Isa. 58.7. Dan. 4.27. Luka 11.41; 12.33. Jak. 2.15,16. 1 Joha. 3.17.\x*.
\v 12 Kwasekufika labathelisi ukuze babhabhathizwe\x + 7.29. Mat. 18.17.\x*, basebesithi kuye: Mfundisi, sizakwenzani\x + 3.12,14. Seb. 2.37. Seb. 9.6; 16.30; 22.10.\x*?
\v 13 Wasesithi kubo: Lingabizi okwedlula elikumiselweyo\x + 19.23. 19.8.\x*.
\v 14 Lamabutho lawo ambuza, athi: Thina-ke sizakwenzani\x + 3.12,14. Seb. 2.37. Seb. 9.6; 16.30; 22.10.\x*? Wasesithi kuwo: Lingenzi udlakela\f + \fk udlakela: \fl kumbe, \fq lingesabisi umuntu\f* emuntwini, njalo lingacali ngamanga\x + Levi 19.11. Luka 19.8. Eks. 23.1.\x*; njalo yeneliswani yimivuzo yenu\x + Roma 6.23. 2 Kor. 11.8.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Kwathi abantu belindile, futhi bonke bezibuza enhliziyweni zabo ngoJohane, ukuthi kambe yena angaba enguKristu\x + Joha. 1.19,20.\x*,
\v 16 uJohane waphendula, esithi kubo bonke: Mina-ke ngilibhabhathiza ngamanzi; kodwa uyeza olamandla kulami, engingafanele ukuthukulula umchilo wamanyathela akhe\x + Mark. 1.7.\x*; yena uzalibhabhathiza ngoMoya oNgcwele langomlilo;
\v 17 okhomane lwakhe lokwela lusesandleni sakhe, njalo uzahlambululisisa isibuya sakhe, abesebuthela amabele esiphaleni sakhe\x + Mat. 6.26; 13.30. Luka 12.18,24.\x*, kodwa amakhoba uzawatshisa ngomlilo ongacitshekiyo.
\p
\v 18 Langokulaya ngezinye izinto ezinengi, watshumayela ivangeli ebantwini.
\v 19 Kodwa\x + Mat. 14.3. Mark. 6.17. Joha. 3.24.\x* uHerodi umtetrarki\x + 3.1.\x*, owayesolwe nguye ngoHerodiyasi umkaFiliphu umfowabo\x + 3.1.\x*, langakho konke okubi ayekwenzile uHerodi,
\v 20 wengezelela lalokhu phezu kwakho konke, ukuthi wamvalela uJohane entolongweni.
\s Ukubhabhathizwa kukaJesu
\p
\v 21 Kwasekusithi sebebhabhathiziwe bonke abantu, laye uJesu esebhabhathiziwe\x + 3.21,22, Mat. 3.13-17. Mark. 1.9-11.\x*, ekhuleka\x + 9.28,29. 6.12.\x*, izulu lavulwa,
\v 22 uMoya oyiNgcwele wasesehlela phezu kwakhe elesimo somzimba onjengowejuba, lelizwi lavela ezulwini, lisithi: Wena uyiNdodana yami ethandekayo, ngithokoza ngawe.
\s Okhokho bakaJesu
\p
\v 23 Yena uJesu waseqala ukuba leminyaka engaba ngamatshumi amathathu\x + Nani 4.3.\x*, \add yena\add* (njengokwakunakanwa) eyindodana kaJosefa\x + 4.22. Joha. 6.42.\x*, kaEli,
